    "description": "We at Beyond Wildlife India are looking for an experienced Reservation Manager based out of Bhopal. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Beyond Wildlife India:\nBeyond Wildlife India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Beyond Wildlife India!",
